=== TITLE
issue #58 

=== DESCRIPTION
since extending ignores all non-block bodies, the import statement (that is executed at runtime) does not reach.

=== INPUT
{}

=== TEMPLATE:main
{% extends "layout" %}
{% import "macros" as macros %}
{% block body %}
{{ macros.foo(1, 2, 3) }}
{% endblock %}

=== TEMPLATE:layout
{% block body %}
{% endblock %}

=== TEMPLATE:macros
{% macro foo(a, b, c) %}
	{{- "#{a}, #{b}, #{c}" -}}
{% endmacro %}

=== OUTPUT
1, 2, 3
